# Corona Theme - Obsidian Theme Development Rules

## Context7 Documentation

When working on this Obsidian theme, always fetch the latest Obsidian theme documentation from Context7 to ensure accurate implementation of theme properties and CSS variables.

- [[calls]]
  match = "when working on Obsidian theme files, CSS variables, or theme.css modifications"
  tool = "context7"
  library = "/websites/help_obsidian_md"
  url = "https://context7.com/websites/obsidian_md"

## Project Preferences

- This is an Obsidian theme located in `.obsidian/themes/Corona`
- Use CSS custom properties over SCSS variables when possible
- Use OKLCH color space for color-mix functions
- Keep `tokens.scss` minimal with only import statements
